question: Eric has three times as many TikTok friends as Alex. Ashley has two times as many friends on TikTok as Alex. If Eric has 200 friends on TikTok, how many TikTok friends does Ashley have?
answer:
Alex has 200/3 = <<200/3=66>>66 TikTok friends.
Ashley has 2*66 = <<2*66=133>>133 TikTok friends.
#### 133
